snippet.title: Spookynakki - Clear level after level of monsters, using the blocks you stand on as your weapon!
snippet.description:
Play for free on itch.io https://team-bugulon.itch.io/spookynakki?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt Clear level after level of monsters, using the very blocks you stand on as your only weapon. Can you defeat every foe without falling through the shrinking foundation?

Spookynakki is the bone-chilling continuation of Grabanakki, featuring 3 new worlds, a variety of new and returning mechanics, and a completely new OST.

➡️ More from Team Bugulon https://team-bugulon.itch.io/?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt
➡️ More 2D platformers https://itch.io/games/genre-platformer?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt
